**Findings**
1. `高` 数据范围控制只修到了 `GET /tasks`，其余明细/提交/统计端点仍可绕过。设计要求 `parent` 只能看自己孩子、`grade_leader` 只能看本年级、`homeroom_teacher` 只能看本班、`subject_teacher` 受更细 scope 限制，但路由实现里只有列表接口加了 `assigned_by` / `class_id` 处理，`get_task`、`list_submissions`、`submit_homework`、`grade_single`、`grade_batch`、`get_stats` 都只校验“同校存在”后直接放行。这意味着有 `VIEW_HOMEWORK` 的角色理论上可以越权查看或操作不属于自己的作业/提交。见 [设计文档](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-design.md:158), [设计文档](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-design.md:185), [实施计划](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-plan.md:1423), [实施计划](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-plan.md:1445), [实施计划](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-plan.md:1515), [实施计划](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-plan.md:1527), [实施计划](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-plan.md:1554), [实施计划](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-plan.md:1568)。

2. `高` F-06 只改了类型，没有把 `deadline` 真正接入创建接口。`TaskCreate.deadline` 已改成 `datetime`，但 `POST /tasks` 调用 `HomeworkTaskService.create_task()` 时没有传 `req.deadline`，导致 API 创建的作业会静默丢失截止时间，后续 `expired` 语义也失真。见 [实施计划](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-plan.md:1344), [实施计划](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-plan.md:1403), [实施计划](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-plan.md:1407), [实施计划](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-plan.md:502)。

3. `中高` F-05 在计划里改成了 `read/write`，但设计文档还残留 `homework.assign` / `homework.grade`。Agent 工具表和 capability 矩阵仍按三种 action 描述，和计划里的 `requires_capabilities={"homework.write"}` 直接冲突；实现者按设计落地会接错 capability。见 [设计文档](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-design.md:101), [设计文档](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-design.md:198), [设计文档](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-design.md:229), [实施计划](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-plan.md:1679), [实施计划](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-plan.md:1861)。

4. `中` `principal` 的权限边界在 3 份文档里不一致。设计文档把 `principal` 放进 `manage_homework`，而实施计划只给 `principal` 加 `VIEW_HOMEWORK`，默认 capability 也只有 `homework.read`；这又和项目规则里“校长=全校管理+分析”相冲突。这个差异会直接导致后续 RBAC 实现无法判定哪个版本才是正确需求。见 [设计文档](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-design.md:88), [实施计划](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-plan.md:280), [实施计划](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-plan.md:300), [CLAUDE.md](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/CLAUDE.md:277)。

5. `中` `create_task` 的校验契约没有真正落地。设计文档写了 `exam_id` 存在性检查和 `assigned_by` 归属校验，测试边界也列了 `exam_id="nonexistent"`，但计划中的实现只检查“`post_exam` 是否提供了 `exam_id`”，完全没有做存在性/归属性验证。这会把业务错误推迟成数据库异常，且 `assigned_by` 的越校归属问题仍未处理。见 [设计文档](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-design.md:100), [实施计划](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-plan.md:487), [实施计划](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-plan.md:489), [实施计划](C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/docs/plans/2026-03-30-phase2.2-homework-system-plan.md:629)。

